them are the protectors of His\\ncreatures and guards of the doors of the gardens of Paradise.\",{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1060,\"props\":1243,\"children\":1244},{},[1245],{\"type\":1068,\"value\":1246},\"Among them are those also whose steps are fixed on earth but their necks\\nare protruding into the skies, their limbs are getting out on all sides,\\ntheir shoulders are in accord with the columns of the Divine Throne,\\ntheir eyes are downcast before it, they have spread down their wings\\nunder it and they have rendered between themselves and all else curtains\\nof honour and screens of power.\",{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1060,\"props\":1248,\"children\":1249},{},[1250],{\"type\":1068,\"value\":1251},\"They do not think of their Creator through image, do not impute to Him\\nattributes of the created, do not confine Him within abodes and do not\\npoint at Him through illustrations.\",{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1078,\"props\":1253,\"children\":1254},{},[1255],{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1060,\"props\":1256,\"children\":1257},{},[1258],{\"type\":1068,\"value\":1259},\"ثُمَّ فَتَقَ مَا بَيْنَ السَّمواتِ العُلاَ، فَمَلاَهُنَّ أَطْواراً مِنْ مَلائِكَتِهِ:\",{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1078,\"props\":1261,\"children\":1262},{},[1263],{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1060,\"props\":1264,\"children\":1265},{},[1266],{\"type\":1068,\"value\":1267},\"مِنْهُمْ سُجُودٌ لاَيَرْكَعُونَ، وَرُكُوعٌ لاَ يَنْتَصِبُونَ، وَصَافُّونَ لاَ يَتَزَايَلُونَ، وَمُسَبِّحُونَ لاَ\\nيَسْأَمُونَ، لاَ يَغْشَاهُمْ نَوْمُ العُيُونِ، وَلاَ سَهْوُ العُقُولِ، وَلاَ فَتْرَةُ الاَبْدَانِ، ولاَ\\nغَفْلَةُ النِّسْيَانِ.\",{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1078,\"props\":1269,\"children\":1270},{},[1271],{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1060,\"props\":1272,\"children\":1273},{},[1274],{\"type\":1068,\"value\":1275},\"وَمِنْهُمْ أُمَنَاءُ عَلَى وَحْيِهِ، وأَلسِنَةٌ إِلَى رُسُلِهِ، وَمُخْتَلِفُونَ بِقَضَائِهِ وَأَمْرهِ.\",{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1078,\"props\":1277,\"children\":1278},{},[1279],{\"type\":1059,\"tag\":1060,\"props\":1280,\"children\":1281},{},[